				<td colspan="2"><span>Hiya folks, I'm coming back to my bard after an extended break to play my beastlord and I have a couple of quick questions.  
<br />

<br />
1.  I need a lute.  Is the Lute of the Howler still worth the 25k to 30k that it sells for on Inny or is there something better out there that is easily camped or quested?
<br />

<br />
2.  What dungeons should I be concentrating on in LDoN?  I've tried to use LDoN merchant webpage but it's down again and I don't know of any other sites out there that list gear sold by the merchants.
<br />

<br />
I appreciate any help you might be able to offer:)</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
