				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Coming back to the bard<a name="15175"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 12 04 7:55 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>No way Howler Lute is worth 25k.  The illusion effect is a toy, nothing more.  Yes it does buff you and gives you some haste, but you can get a better haste buff from a chanter or shaman pretty easy.  Unless you rarely group with a chanter or shaman, or even a beastlord, the effects the illustion grants arent worth that.  You can even sing yourself better haste.
<br />
The mod on it is good, but you can get a similar mod lute a LOT cheaper.
<br />
10k maybe, cause it is a decent mod, primary held, illusion/buff effect lute.  But 25k or more?  No way.</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
