				<td colspan="2"><span>Lute of the Howler is definately not worth that.  I think the price has inflated (it is that much on my server) because there has not been a lot of activity in Velks and the fact that this Lute is the only Primary non-NO DROP lute around.
<br />

<br />
I am going to start trying to get LDoN adventures in EC (Ruj brand) so that I can earn points to get the Rujarkian Lute of Battle (NO DROP / PRIMARY / 2.6 mod for 524(approx) AP).  So if you were looking to get a lute, that would be a good adventure site to head to.
<br />

<br />
Good luck.
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
