<br />

<br />
Do No Ro adventures to buy the 1492 points plate armor.
<br />

<br />
So at lvl 65 do 10 in EC and 30 in No Ro and then do them wherever. To get more armor.
<br />

<br />
You could skip the lute. I only use it in down time and that is not often.
