				<td colspan="2"><span>Mod on lute wont affect mana regen for mana song.  It will affect hp regen though.
<br />

<br />
The clickie effect of howler lute wont stack with predator buffs.  I would rather have predator buffs.  The ATK is nice though, but I have yet to see ATK having a huge impact on my DPS.
<br />

<br />
For most bards, this iute is, as I said, a toy.  With the cash required to buy the lute, you could be gear that would give you permanent effects that stack, and are better then the buffs from the lute.
<br />

<br />
I dont know about the zek or RP servers, but on a blue server, I cant in good consience advise young bards to spend a lot of cash on this
